title: Alex.Jones.Show.2008.06.27-chakra71
description:
Friday June 27, 2008

Alex talks with Oklahoma Republican state representative Charles Key who authored a resolution reasserting Oklahoma's sovereignty under the Tenth Amendment to the U.S. Constitution. As well, Alex welcomes back researcher and independent scholar Jordan Maxwell to talk about the occult and secret societies.

Four hours duration before commercial edit takes it down to just over 3 hours of playing time.

Includes discussion during commercials.

Note, the stream cut off the last minute and a half from the 4th hour.  Not sure why, but that's the way the live stream came in.  Sorry!
